title: Thom Hartmann Program - January 30 2014
description:
January 30, 2014
The Thom Hartmann Program

Hour One: Who is full of "bull-shevik?"  Fred Siegel, The Revolt Against The Masses: How Liberalism Has Undermined The Middle Class  / Plus, the middle class is toast...

Hour Two: An out of control Pharma?  Mike Papantonio, Ring of Fire Radio  / Stop Trade Treachery!  Congressman Alan Grayson (D-FL, 9th District)

Hour Three: Time for Big Oil to pay for its pollution... / Plus, Geeky Science - pesticide link to brain disease
